
###################################################################
# BEGIN: lab-program README
###################################################################

A Makefile has been added to simplify the running of the relevant
test scenario's. 

  [1] Usage is displayed by running the Makefile with no options. 

      > make             -> display below usage details.

        ==================================================
        Usage:
          > make test_index       - see test list below
          > make clean            - run CLEAN script
          > make regress          - run all tests and generate summary
          > make summary          - generate summary

            -----------------------------------------
            test_index      test_name
            -----------------------------------------
            t1              counter_sanity_check
            t2              counter_count2max
            t3              counter_count2max_bug
            t4              counter_disable_count
            t5              counter_reset_count
            t6              counter_reset_disable
            t7              counter_preload
            t8              counter_count2max_detect
        ================================================== 

  [2] To run a particular testcase use the test_index

      > make t1          -> runs test t1 (counter_sanity_check)
      > make t8          -> runs test t8 (counter_count2max_detect)

  [3] To run CLEAN script to remove generated directories and file

      > make clean       -> runs CLEAN script

###################################################################
# END: lab-program README
